The paper deals with image restoration, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The participating media mentioned in the abstract (fog, turbid water, sand storm) are often encountered in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications. The use of image formation models and priors suggests a machine learning (cs.AI) or statistical learning (cs.LG) approach.
